":guilabel:`Diamond`."
msgstr "插值值按线性计算（每步数值相等）。图标：:guilabel:`菱形` 。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid "Constant"
msgstr "常量"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid ""
"Interpolated values stay the same until the next key frame, and jump to the "
"new value. Icon: :guilabel:`Square`."
msgstr "插值值保持不变直到下一个关键帧，然后跳变到新值。图标：:guilabel:`方形` 。"

