# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:77
msgid "Timing"
msgstr "时间控制"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:78
msgid ""
"Changing how fast a clip plays is done with the :guilabel:`Time` property "
"and the :guilabel:`Timing` tool."
msgstr "调整剪辑播放速度可通过 :guilabel:`时间` 属性和 :guilabel:` 时间控制` 工具完成。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:80
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Time` menu offers presets such as normal, fast, slow, freeze,"
" and reverse. See details in :ref:`clip_time_ref`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`时间` 菜单提供正常、快速、慢速、冻结和反向等预设。详情见 :ref:`clip_time_ref` 。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:81
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Timing` tool lets you drag a clip’s edges to speed it up or "
"slow it down. OpenShot adds the needed Time keyframes and **scales your "
"other keyframes** so your animations stay aligned. Shorter clips play "
"faster, longer clips play slower. See more: :ref:`clip_time_ref`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`时间控制` 工具允许拖动剪辑边缘以加快或减慢速度。OpenShot 会自动添加所需的时间关键帧，并**缩放其他关键帧** "
"，确保动画保持同步。剪辑越短播放越快，越长播放越慢。详情见 :ref:`clip_time_ref` 。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:86
msgid "Repeating"
msgstr "重复播放"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:87
msgid ""
"To play a clip multiple times, use :guilabel:`Right-Click → Time → Repeat`."
msgstr "要多次播放剪辑，请使用 :guilabel:`右键点击 → 时间 → 重复` 。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:89
msgid ":guilabel:`Loop` repeats in one direction (forward or reverse)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`循环` 在一个方向（正向或反向）重复播放。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Ping-Pong` alternates direction (forward then backward, etc.)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`乒乓` 交替方向播放（先正向再反向，依此类推）。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom` can add a short pause between passes, speed up or slow "
"down each pass, including keyframes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`自定义` 可在循环间添加短暂停顿，加速或减慢每次循环，包括关键帧。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:93
msgid ""
"OpenShot writes the :guilabel:`Time` curve for you, and you can edit those "
"keyframes just like any other. See more: :ref:`clip_time_repeat_ref`."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot 会为你生成 :guilabel:`时间` 曲线，你可以像编辑其他关键帧一样编辑这些关键帧。详情见 "
":ref:`clip_time_repeat_ref` 。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:97
msgid "Bézier Presets"
msgstr "贝塞尔预设"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:98
msgid ""
"When using a Bézier curve for animation, OpenShot includes more than 20 "
"curve presets (which affect the shape of the curve). For example, **Ease-"
"In** has a more gradual slope at the beginning, making an animation move "
"slower at the beginning, and faster at the end. **Ease-In/Out (Back)** has a"
" gradual beginning and ending, but actually goes past the expected value and"
" then back (producing a bounce effect)."
msgstr ""
"当使用贝塞尔曲线进行动画时，OpenShot 包含超过 20 种曲线预设（影响曲线形状）。例如，**Ease-In** "
"在开始时斜率更缓，使动画开始时移动较慢，结束时加快。**Ease-In/Out (Back)** "
"在开始和结束时都较为缓和，但实际上会超过预期值然后回弹（产生弹跳效果）。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:103
msgid ""
"To choose a curve preset, right click on the small graph icon next to a key "
"frame."
msgstr "要选择曲线预设，请右键点击关键帧旁的小图表图标。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:110
msgid "Image Sequences"
msgstr "图像序列"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:111
msgid ""
"If you have a sequence of similarly named images (such as, cat001.png, "
"cat002.png, cat003.png, etc...), you can simply drag and drop one of them "
"into OpenShot, and you will be prompted to import the entire sequence. "
"OpenShot will playback these sequential images rapidly, as if they are "
"frames in a video. The rate or speed in which these images are displayed is "
"based on their frame rate."
msgstr ""
"如果您有一系列名称相似的图像（例如 cat001.png、cat002.png、cat003.png 等），只需将其中一个拖放到 OpenShot "
"中，系统会提示您导入整个序列。OpenShot 会快速播放这些连续图像，就像视频中的帧一样。图像显示的速率基于其帧率。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:116
msgid ""
"**NOTE:** Be sure your image sequence starts at 0 or 1, or you will likely "
"receive an error when importing it into OpenShot. For example, if your "
"sequence starts at cat222.png, or has missing images in the sequence, "
"OpenShot will struggle to understand the sequence. An easy work-around is to"
" renumber the images so they start with 1."
msgstr ""
"**注意：** 确保您的图像序列从 0 或 1 开始，否则导入 OpenShot 时可能会出错。例如，如果序列从 cat222.png "
"开始，或序列中缺少图像，OpenShot 将难以识别该序列。一个简单的解决方法是重新编号图像，使其从 1 开始。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:122
msgid ""
"To adjust the frame rate of the animation, right click and choose **File "
"Properties** in the **Project Files** panel, and adjust the frame rate. Once"
" you have set the correct frame rate, drag the animation onto the timeline."
msgstr "要调整动画的帧率，请在“项目文件”面板中右键点击并选择 **文件属性** ，然后调整帧率。设置正确的帧率后，将动画拖到时间轴上。"

